name: Mr. Fresh Crewneck Sweatshirt
description:
Exclusive to the WTF? Apparel Spring/Summer 13 collection. 

WTF? Apparel "Mr. Fresh" crewneck features a large Mr.Fresh graphic on the front. Garment is lovingly screenprinted in the UK on a super soft purple heather raglan crewneck. 

❤ Lightweight crew neck
❤ Slim fit
❤ Soft feel lightweight fabric
❤ Set in Sleeves
❤ Ribbed collar, cuff and hem
❤ Taped Neck
❤ Stitched V detail at neck
❤ Hidden ear phone loops
❤ (WRAP) certified production

Crewneck measurements:
S - 36' / M - 40' / L - 44' / XL - 48' 

Any questions contact us through the contact page and we'll be happy to answer 'em!
